ji\" /> 個人好樣衰呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係呀，兩公婆咁樣真係</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739f7b328da7705965957f93dcb49211b046e69a","tid":236572,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"我就準時十一點前訓得著^.^<br />\n跟住8點起身溫豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148100c492f609fc9b644202ae63258baec01fc2","tid":236572,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人好樣衰呀</blockquote><br />\n都唔關你事既<br />\n你老豆老母問題啫"},{"pid":"aa818bb0b58bbd256d73d00ef7fff12cbfda7cd3","tid":236572,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人好樣衰呀</blockquote><br />\n都唔關你事既<br />\n你老豆老母問題啫</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母<br />\n今次撐小馬"},{"pid":"eae02a3fab78ed25f1b3a13f817a4e415b79884b","tid":236572,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人好樣衰呀</blockquote><br />\n都唔關你事既<br />\n你老豆老母問題啫</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母<br />\n今次撐小馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食屎，小馬不知幾靚<br />\n校園台Emma wa