072a411fc7ec060ff72858","tid":236572,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人好樣衰呀</blockquote><br />\n都唔關你事既<br />\n你老豆老母問題啫</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母<br />\n今次撐小馬</blockquote><br />\n小雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f01020838269a93682ebfc868f10d0adb22497","tid":236572,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人好樣衰呀</blockquote><br />\n都唔關你事既<br />\n你老豆老母問題啫</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母<br />\n今次撐小馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食屎，小馬不知幾靚<br />\n校園台Emma watson</blockquote><br />\n你係校園台山崎賢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1f5896e823ad51c8d5a461c5d076c4cb7434b2","tid":236572,"uid":107233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:15:36.000Z","msg":"我都係... 睇過精神科 冇用"},{"pid":"72f3144805348ca576e9bc5f4c5da40fdb310125","tid":236572,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:14:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係... 睇過精神科 冇用</blockquote><br />\n真係惡夢<br />\n屋企人成日鬧我夜訓 叫我早d訓<br />\n但屌啦 訓唔著呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396c18659a6074fc3525199ed5f3f8917781f676","tid":236572,"uid":42379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T18:15:05.000Z","msg":"頭髮甩曬未"},{"pid":"eb195